item.dc:creator: @Yoshi0308 Yoshi0308
item.description:
@Yoshi0308 wrote:

Start > All Programs > Accessories > System Tools > System Restore.

Restore your computer to the latest time before you deleted your ISP or whatever. It worked for me.

EDIT: By the way, this isn’t an off-topic question.
